title: CeraVe Moisturizing Cream, Two 2 Ounce Tubes
description: CeraVe moisturizing cream is a vital part of a daily skin care routine. Its patented MVE formulation releases ceramides and other essential ingredients throughout the day, so they penetrate deep into the skin to hydrate and nourish.

title: CoverGirl Outlast Lipstain Nude Kiss 427
description: The water-based colorants of Outlast Lipstain give lips a beautiful, lightweight flush of color that won't come off, lasting for hours without the heavy look or feel of an ordinary lipstick. Its pen-like precision applicator makes it easy to define your lips-just draw on color without any hassle!
